1
00:00:26,784 --> 00:00:27,565
I'll be right there.

2
00:00:29,344 --> 00:00:29,804
Son,

3
00:00:30,225 --> 00:00:31,725
give me some money.

4
00:00:32,405 --> 00:00:33,925
I want to buy some wine.

5
00:00:34,164 --> 00:00:34,624
Why are you here?

6
00:00:35,164 --> 00:00:35,964
I... I don't have any money.

7
00:00:36,405 --> 00:00:37,605
You bought such expensive flowers,

8
00:00:37,865 --> 00:00:38,705
and you say you don't have money?

9
00:00:39,324 --> 00:00:40,245
Look, everyone.

10
00:00:41,245 --> 00:00:42,425
You... let go of me!

11
00:00:42,925 --> 00:00:43,565
Look,

12
00:00:43,805 --> 00:00:44,945
this is an unfilial son.

13
00:00:47,544 --> 00:00:48,245
Sorry to keep you waiting.

14
00:00:48,864 --> 00:00:49,224
Let's go.

15
00:00:49,464 --> 00:00:50,925
I found another great restaurant today.

16
00:00:51,245 --> 00:00:52,025
Take me there.

17
00:00:52,105 --> 00:00:52,824
Look,

18
00:00:53,205 --> 00:00:54,764
this is how he treats his father.

19
00:00:54,945 --> 00:00:55,925
What a bad son!

20
00:01:10,824 --> 00:01:11,224
Hey,

21
00:01:11,904 --> 00:01:12,525
our young lady is

22
00:01:12,544 --> 00:01:13,904
the heir to Chenghai Group.

23
00:01:14,385 --> 00:01:15,684
Your life has been

24
00:01:15,684 --> 00:01:16,564
laid out since birth.

25
00:01:18,105 --> 00:01:18,964
Your life

26
00:01:19,225 --> 00:01:20,464
is doomed to be different from hers.

27
00:01:21,264 --> 00:01:21,885
Of course,

28
00:01:22,285 --> 00:01:23,445
if you have any needs,

29
00:01:23,865 --> 00:01:25,044
you can also make your conditions.

30
00:02:21,785 --> 00:02:23,584
Your wound will get inflamed if it gets wet.

31
00:02:24,584 --> 00:02:25,484
Let me help you.

32
00:02:39,505 --> 00:02:40,044
No, thanks.

33
00:02:41,764 --> 00:02:42,824
I can do it myself.

34
00:02:49,764 --> 00:02:52,285
I'll go take a shower first.

35
00:03:06,465 --> 00:03:07,524
The night is windy and humid.

36
00:03:08,764 --> 00:03:10,345
Don't go to the greenhouse alone.

37
00:03:13,764 --> 00:03:14,864
I'll be worried.

38
00:03:16,764 --> 00:03:17,324
Okay.

39
00:03:18,524 --> 00:03:19,044
Okay.

40
00:03:22,204 --> 00:03:22,984
Go.

41
00:03:26,165 --> 00:03:27,544
Don't catch a cold.

42
00:03:50,165 --> 00:03:50,605
Sir.

43
00:03:51,285 --> 00:03:51,744
I've searched everywhere.

44
00:03:52,125 --> 00:03:53,165
Nothing unusual was found.

45
00:03:56,864 --> 00:03:57,704
How many flowers were damaged?

46
00:03:58,445 --> 00:03:59,445
Replace them before dawn.

47
00:03:59,885 --> 00:04:00,924
Don't let the lady find out.

48
00:04:01,364 --> 00:04:01,785
Yes.

49
00:04:02,945 --> 00:04:03,465
By the way,

50
00:04:04,044 --> 00:04:04,864
keep an eye on

51
00:04:05,405 --> 00:04:05,924
the flower girl.

52
00:04:06,405 --> 00:04:07,285
Don't let her get close to my wife.

53
00:04:07,764 --> 00:04:08,125
Sir,

54
00:04:08,565 --> 00:04:09,725
do you suspect that she is the killer

55
00:04:09,744 --> 00:04:10,524
recruited from the website?

56
00:04:21,885 --> 00:04:23,924
Excuse me, are you looking for me?

57
00:04:28,044 --> 00:04:29,304
Do you know Ye Zhimei?

58
00:04:39,645 --> 00:04:41,645
I've confirmed with the search and rescue team.

59
00:04:41,864 --> 00:04:43,044
The first person to find you

60
00:04:43,044 --> 00:04:44,424
was your fake husband.

61
00:04:44,944 --> 00:04:46,225
You're right.

62
00:04:46,225 --> 00:04:48,205
He was there when the accident happened.

63
00:04:48,205 --> 00:04:49,705
He may be involved in it.

64
00:04:50,124 --> 00:04:52,504
Zhi Mei, what should we do next?

65
00:04:54,265 --> 00:04:57,225
Whether you want to rob or kill,

66
00:04:57,725 --> 00:04:59,004
no matter what your purpose is,

67
00:05:00,165 --> 00:05:01,845
I won't let you succeed.

68
00:05:03,465 --> 00:05:04,345
You must search carefully.

69
00:05:04,504 --> 00:05:05,845
The customer paid a lot of money.

70
00:05:05,864 --> 00:05:06,725
Find it back.

71
00:05:07,044 --> 00:05:07,304
Yes.

72
00:05:15,184 --> 00:05:15,684
Over there.

73
00:05:17,705 --> 00:05:19,225
This time, you should be able to eat it.

74
00:05:20,564 --> 00:05:21,345
Xiaomei.

75
00:05:24,265 --> 00:05:25,405
Zhang Wei.

76
00:05:25,624 --> 00:05:26,825
You're back from abroad.

77
00:05:32,624 --> 00:05:33,205
Let me.

78
00:05:35,944 --> 00:05:36,684
Zhang Wei.

79
00:05:46,085 --> 00:05:46,504
Hello.

80
00:05:54,585 --> 00:05:55,465
You must be my brother-in-law.

81
00:05:56,585 --> 00:05:56,944
Wu Xi.

82
00:05:59,165 --> 00:06:00,085
I finally meet you.

83
00:06:00,424 --> 00:06:01,744
I often hear Xiaomei talk about you.

84
00:06:03,484 --> 00:06:03,905
Hello.

85
00:06:04,544 --> 00:06:05,085
I'm Zhang Wei.

86
00:06:22,525 --> 00:06:23,304
Xiaomei,

87
00:06:23,944 --> 00:06:24,785
I'm back this time

88
00:06:24,924 --> 00:06:25,825
not only to see you,

89
00:06:26,364 --> 00:06:26,944
but also

90
00:06:27,424 --> 00:06:28,444
because the annual audit and reconciliation process

91
00:06:28,465 --> 00:06:30,624
of the trust fund has already started.

92
00:06:31,105 --> 00:06:32,585
Here are some documents that need your signature.

93
00:06:32,605 --> 00:06:34,244
You have to sign them in person.

94
00:06:38,465 --> 00:06:38,785
Thank you.

95
00:06:45,504 --> 00:06:47,145
It's okay, Zhang Wei.

96
00:06:47,285 --> 00:06:48,405
There are no secrets

97
00:06:48,624 --> 00:06:49,465
between my husband and me.

98
00:07:09,624 --> 00:07:10,225
But

99
00:07:11,364 --> 00:07:12,465
since Zhang Wei is here,

100
00:07:12,765 --> 00:07:13,804
I have an important matter

101
00:07:14,364 --> 00:07:15,364
that I need to decide on now.

102
00:07:17,244 --> 00:07:17,785
What is it?

103
00:07:18,585 --> 00:07:19,744
I want to make a will today.

104
00:07:26,484 --> 00:07:26,944
Honey,

105
00:07:28,484 --> 00:07:30,205
I hope you can support me.

106
00:07:39,004 --> 00:07:40,304
Ye Zhimei sent me to you.

107
00:07:41,364 --> 00:07:42,525
I know it's hard to believe,

108
00:07:43,325 --> 00:07:44,705
but she's being held captive

109
00:07:44,705 --> 00:07:45,965
by a man who pretends to be Wu Xi.

110
00:07:46,484 --> 00:07:47,645
How is that possible?

111
00:07:49,544 --> 00:07:50,665
After I dealt with

112
00:07:50,665 --> 00:07:51,905
the inheritance of Uncle Ye and Auntie Ye,

113
00:07:52,304 --> 00:07:53,845
I've been in charge of overseas business.

114
00:07:54,124 --> 00:07:55,364
I just had time to come back to China recently.

115
00:07:56,444 --> 00:07:57,884
I haven't even had time to contact her yet.

116
00:07:59,544 --> 00:08:00,465
What should we do?

117
00:08:01,025 --> 00:08:01,785
We should rescue her.

118
00:08:02,205 --> 00:08:03,265
Meimei said

119
00:08:03,765 --> 00:08:05,605
her husband Wu Xi died under mysterious circumstances.

120
00:08:06,265 --> 00:08:07,744
She wants to stay with that man

121
00:08:07,924 --> 00:08:09,105
to find concrete evidence.

122
00:08:09,265 --> 00:08:09,684
No way.

123
00:08:10,184 --> 00:08:11,265
It's too dangerous.

124
00:08:11,645 --> 00:08:12,424
Don't underestimate her.

125
00:08:13,564 --> 00:08:14,564
She's braver and smarter

126
00:08:14,585 --> 00:08:15,544
than we thought.

127
00:08:16,165 --> 00:08:17,384
The only thing we can do now

128
00:08:17,765 --> 00:08:19,004
is to cooperate with her plan.

129
00:08:32,845 --> 00:08:33,544
Zhimei,

130
00:08:34,605 --> 00:08:35,364
isn't it too early

131
00:08:35,765 --> 00:08:36,884
to make a will now?

132
00:08:37,384 --> 00:08:38,585
Better safe than sorry.

133
00:08:39,145 --> 00:08:40,504
I just want to

134
00:08:40,504 --> 00:08:41,705
provide you with some security.

135
00:08:43,264 --> 00:08:43,884
You'll support me,

136
00:08:43,984 --> 00:08:44,764
right?

137
00:08:50,904 --> 00:08:51,685
We can start now.

138
00:08:51,685 --> 00:08:52,105
Okay.

139
00:08:54,425 --> 00:08:54,845
I,

140
00:08:55,624 --> 00:08:56,305
Ye Zimei,

141
00:08:56,764 --> 00:08:58,004
hereby declare,

142
00:08:59,345 --> 00:09:01,744
should anything happen to me in the future,

143
00:09:02,685 --> 00:09:04,404
all my personal property

144
00:09:05,024 --> 00:09:05,884
will be inherited

145
00:09:06,425 --> 00:09:07,164
Wu Xi,

146
00:09:07,605 --> 00:09:08,465
my husband.

147
00:09:09,585 --> 00:09:10,124
Moreover,

148
00:09:10,664 --> 00:09:11,264
I decide that

149
00:09:11,984 --> 00:09:13,764
if my husband Wu Xi

150
00:09:14,024 --> 00:09:15,904
can't inherit my property because of death,

151
00:09:16,605 --> 00:09:17,484
all my property

152
00:09:17,945 --> 00:09:18,925
will be donated

153
00:09:18,945 --> 00:09:20,445
to a charitable organization

154
00:09:21,465 --> 00:09:24,305
without any other heirs.

155
00:09:31,185 --> 00:09:31,864
Okay.

156
00:09:47,244 --> 00:09:47,845
Have we met before

157
00:09:47,845 --> 00:09:49,805
at Zhimei's graduation ceremony?

158
00:09:50,764 --> 00:09:51,884
I'm afraid you're wrong.

159
00:09:52,565 --> 00:09:53,225
I've been abroad

160
00:09:53,585 --> 00:09:54,605
dealing with some

161
00:09:54,624 --> 00:09:55,925
tricky cases in the past few years.

162
00:09:56,864 --> 00:09:58,425
I should have visited you earlier,

163
00:09:58,425 --> 00:09:59,404
but I didn't.

164
00:09:59,764 --> 00:10:00,644
I'm sorry.

165
00:10:00,884 --> 00:10:01,685
Really?

166
00:10:03,065 --> 00:10:04,845
Zhimei always told me that

167
00:10:05,484 --> 00:10:06,605
you two were very close when you were young.

168
00:10:07,305 --> 00:10:08,565
It seems that you've become

169
00:10:09,465 --> 00:10:10,644
you've grown apart.

170
00:10:12,164 --> 00:10:15,305
As Xiaomei's half-brother,

171
00:10:15,864 --> 00:10:16,685
I'm kindly reminding you

172
00:10:17,364 --> 00:10:18,205
that Xiaomei doesn't

173
00:10:18,364 --> 00:10:19,325
seem very happy.

174
00:10:19,685 --> 00:10:20,605
You should pay more attention to her.

175
00:10:20,925 --> 00:10:21,524
Take her out more often.

176
00:10:21,524 --> 00:10:22,945
Don't keep her cooped up at home.

177
00:10:23,864 --> 00:10:25,185
Let her get some fresh air.

178
00:10:28,024 --> 00:10:28,465
Honey.

179
00:10:29,065 --> 00:10:29,685
Zhang Wei.

180
00:10:29,685 --> 00:10:30,805
What are you talking about?

181
00:10:31,024 --> 00:10:31,605
We're talking about

182
00:10:32,004 --> 00:10:32,864
the upcoming

183
00:10:32,884 --> 00:10:34,624
anniversary of Mr. and Mrs. Ye's death.

184
00:10:34,925 --> 00:10:35,725
You two should

185
00:10:36,225 --> 00:10:37,024
go pay your respects.

186
00:10:37,884 --> 00:10:38,325
Yeah,

187
00:10:39,164 --> 00:10:40,185
I haven't

188
00:10:40,764 --> 00:10:42,504
visited their graves in a long time.

189
00:10:43,124 --> 00:10:44,144
Near the cemetery,

190
00:10:44,144 --> 00:10:45,244
there's a new resort hotel

191
00:10:45,244 --> 00:10:46,404
opened by Chenghai Group.

192
00:10:47,004 --> 00:10:47,864
Why don't you

193
00:10:48,024 --> 00:10:49,784
stay there for a few days?

194
00:10:50,345 --> 00:10:51,065
Sure.

195
00:10:51,764 --> 00:10:52,445
We can pretend

196
00:10:52,764 --> 00:10:53,825
it's our honeymoon trip.

197
00:10:54,124 --> 00:10:54,404
Honey,

198
00:10:54,764 --> 00:10:55,345
what do you think?

199
00:10:56,364 --> 00:10:57,524
Let's go.

200
00:11:04,364 --> 00:11:05,404
This way, please.

201
00:11:06,404 --> 00:11:08,085
We've arranged a private area

202
00:11:08,085 --> 00:11:09,105
to ensure you can

203
00:11:09,124 --> 00:11:10,205
have a pleasant time.

204
00:11:17,345 --> 00:11:18,045
Zhi Mei,

205
00:11:18,425 --> 00:11:19,945
what exactly is your plan?

206
00:11:20,484 --> 00:11:23,004
If I can't find evidence, I'll create it.

207
00:11:23,705 --> 00:11:25,305
I'm going to force him to take action against me.

208
00:11:36,585 --> 00:11:36,825
Honey,

209
00:11:37,764 --> 00:11:39,445
I want to visit our parents' grave first.

210
00:11:39,764 --> 00:11:40,404
Sure.

211
00:11:52,925 --> 00:11:53,305
Honey,

212
00:11:54,644 --> 00:11:55,205
let's go.

213
00:12:17,984 --> 00:12:18,545
Dad,

214
00:12:19,384 --> 00:12:19,725
Mom,

215
00:12:20,764 --> 00:12:21,545
don't worry,

216
00:12:22,725 --> 00:12:24,404
I will protect myself.

217
00:12:25,904 --> 00:12:27,965
[Those who see me as prey]

218
00:12:29,325 --> 00:12:30,845
[will surely pay the price.]

219
00:12:41,925 --> 00:12:44,205
How could he know about this?
